<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Account Activation</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .steps { margin: 20px 0; padding-left: 20px; }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; color: #666; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Hello {{name}}!</h2>
        
        <p>Great news! Your account has been successfully activated. You can now create your profile 
        after subscribing to one of our available packages.</p>

        <h3>To get started:</h3>
        <ol class="steps">
            <li>Log in to your account</li>
            <li>Browse our available packages</li>
            <li>Subscribe to a package that suits your needs</li>
            <li>Create your vendor profile</li>
        </ol>

        <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>Your Platform Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>